org.mapsforge.android.maps.overlay
Class OverlayItem

java.lang.Object
  org.mapsforge.android.maps.overlay.OverlayItem

public class OverlayItem
extends Object

OverlayItem holds all parameters of a single element on an ItemizedOverlay, such as position, marker, title and textual description. If the marker is null, the default marker of the overlay will be drawn instead.

setMarker

public void setMarker(android.graphics.drawable.Drawable marker)
Sets the marker that is drawn for this item. If the marker is null, the default marker of the overlay will be drawn instead.

The bounds of the marker must already have been set properly, for example by calling ItemizedOverlay.boundCenterBottom(Drawable).

Changes might not become visible until Overlay.requestRedraw() is called.

Parameters:
marker - the marker that is drawn for this item (may be null).
